caller_intent: The caller (Bessy from Holiday Alliance Insurance) aimed to inform the customer about a canceled homeowner's policy from Travelers and offer reinstatement options.
resolution_steps: Notified the customer of a policy cancellation notice from Travelers.
Offered reinstatement of the policy upon payment of $871.39.
Allowed the customer to request a callback after consulting their sister.
summary: Bessy from Holiday Alliance Insurance informed a customer about a canceled Travelers homeowner's policy and offered reinstatement for $871.39. The customer requested time to consult their sister before proceeding. The call ended with a commitment to follow up.
